doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Stock Running Low

  body
    h1 Stock Running Low
    p Dear Team,
    p The stock for the product #{productName} is running low.
    p Current Stock Level: #{currentStockLevel}
    p Please restock this item as soon as possible to avoid running out of stock.
    p Best regards,
    p The Inventory Management System
